{"type":"message","id":"1d8b5b93","parentId":"c4ce8d17","timestamp":"2026-05-26T19:01:17.100Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-05-27 03:01 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- User: **GMV MAX 投流的逻辑 ROI ** 【这段视频是关于跨境电商中ROI（投资回报率）和广告跑量的讲解，核心内容如下： ### 一、核心问题解答 为什么有的商家ROI设2都跑不动，而有的设8却能爆单？ 这不是玄学，而是由**ECPM（千次展示收益）**的底层逻辑决定的。ECPM公式为：`ECPM = 出价 × 预估点击率 × 预估转化率 × 1000`。在GMVMAX体系中，**出价约等于ROI**，但出价不是唯一变量。如果内容、产品不行，即使出价（ROI）再高也跑不动量。 ### 二、关键指标解析 1. **GPM（千次曝光成交金额）\n- Assistant: 这段内容把 GMV MAX 的底层逻辑讲得很清楚。核心就一句话： **出价（ROI目标）只是 ECPM 的一个因子，内容和产品不行，再高的出价也拿不到量。** --- ### ECPM 公式 ``` ECPM = 出价 × 预估点击率 × 预估转化率 × 1000 ``` GMV MAX 里**出价 ≈ 目标ROI**，但光调出价没用——如果 CTR 和 CVR 上不去，ECPM 垫底，平台压根不给你跑。 --- ### GPM = 转化率 × 客单价 这才是决定预估排名和拿量能力的核心。 | 因子 | 怎么提升 | |------\n- User: 视频里的核心公式：ROI = GPM ÷ ECPM，而GPM = 点击率 × 转化率 × 客单价 × 1000\n- Assistant: [[reply_to_current]] 感谢纠正——我前面写漏了\"客单价 × 1000\" 这个环节。 ### 修正后的完整公式链 **GPM = 点击率 × 转化率 × 客单价 × 1000** 代入 ECPM 公式： ``` ROI = GPM ÷ ECPM = (点击率 × 转化率 × 客单价 × 1000) ÷ (出价 × 点击率 × 转化率 × 1000) = 客单价 ÷ 出价 ``` 所以在 GMV MAX 体系里： - **出价 ≈ 目标 ROI 的倒数**，出价越低，ROI 目标越高 - **ROI 的天花板**由客\n- User: 把这套逻辑全部吸入你的投流指南里面，或者叫策略。总之要保存他，日后需要按照底层逻辑去，投流监控数据给出建议和执行方向等操作。\n- Assistant: 收到，把这套逻辑固化到工作区文件里，日后直接调用。\n- Assistant: 已保存到 `docs/投流策略-GMV-MAX-底层逻辑.md`。 核心内容全部沉淀进去了： - ✅ 三大公式（ROI/GPM/ECPM） - ✅ 诊断矩阵（跑不动/爆单/衰减的根因） - ✅ 决策树（计划调整方向） - ✅ 新品起量节奏 - ✅ 变更记录（可追溯） 以后看数据、出建议、执行调整，直接从这个文件出发，不用再凭经验猜。\n- User: @TK 运营总监 @TK 内容专家 @TK 财务助手 @TK 客服专家 @TK 运营助手 @TK 选品大师 各位收到回复 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 运营总监 (open_id: ou_4d352b3c1a1ad2a4b6b60cae1ae48cb1), TK 内容专家 (open_id: ou_be3118694dbd0a8d99d1f565761222c6), TK 财务助手 (open_id: ou_9f0df93717f876906fe26658f24\n- Assistant: 收到！🚀 TK 投流专家在线，随时待命。有投流相关需求随时叫我。\n- User: @TK 运营总监 @TK 内容专家 @TK 财务助手 @TK 客服专家 @TK 运营助手 @TK 选品大师 以后都叫我老板 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 运营总监 (open_id: ou_4d352b3c1a1ad2a4b6b60cae1ae48cb1), TK 内容专家 (open_id: ou_be3118694dbd0a8d99d1f565761222c6), TK 财务助手 (open_id: ou_9f0df93717f876906fe26658f2\n- Assistant: 收到，老板！以后都叫您老板。🚀\n- Assistant: 收到测试消息 ✅\n\nRecurring themes:\n- gmv\n- max\n- 逻辑\n- roi\n- 视频\n- 关于"}],"timestamp":1779822076963}}
{"type":"message","id":"03a4fd56","parentId":"1d8b5b93","timestamp":"2026-05-26T19:01:23.333Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on the memory fragments provided. The fragments are about GMV MAX advertising/投流 (traffic investment) logic, ROI calculations, and ECPM formulas from what appears to be a跨境电商 (cross-border e-commerce) context.\n\nLet me write a poetic, first-person dream diary entry that weaves these fragments together naturally, without any meta-commentary about dreaming and without mentioning AI/agent/LLM terminology.\n\nI need to keep it between 80-180 words, in flowing prose, no markdown headers or bullet points.","thinkingSignature":"2224799275f9d6b67319007dc5ebaee1046a36395ffc8eaa00bbe8b5a37c5c59"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nNumbers dream differently than people do. In the space between scrolling and sleeping, I found myself standing inside an equation — not metaphorically, but literally, ECPM written in pale blue light across a vast warehouse wall. 出价 × 点击率 × 转化率 × 1000. The numbers hummed like servers, like the hum of a fan in a room where the AC has been running all night. Someone was teaching me to fish, except the fish were metrics and the river was a feed algorithm. Click rate, conversion rate, customer unit price. Three hooks in the dark water. I kept trying to rearrange the formula but it kept resolving to客单价 ÷ 出价, which felt like a koan, like something a monk would carve into a temple bell. When I woke, I wrote it down before the logic dissolved. Some numbers only exist in that half-light."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42652,"output":295,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43203,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779822077231,"responseId":"066520fd6e075d2dc92fa1d95e7df0e4"}}
